### Generate welcome email
POST {{host}}/api/email/generate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "llmMessageBody": "Welcome to **TrustSphere**!\n\nWe're excited to have you join our verified business network. TrustSphere leverages vLEI (Verifiable Legal Entity Identifier) technology to create a trusted ecosystem for digital business interactions.\n\nHere's what you can do with your new account:\n\n- **Verify Your Organization**: Complete your organizational profile and obtain your vLEI credential\n- **Search Verified Companies**: Access our database of verified business entities\n- **Manage Credentials**: Issue, receive, and manage digital credentials\n- **Build Trust**: Establish verified relationships with partners and suppliers\n\nTo get started, please verify your email address and complete your organization's profile. Our AI assistant is available 24/7 to help answer questions about the vLEI ecosystem.\n\n*This is just the beginning of your journey toward trusted digital identity.*",
  "emailTitle": "Welcome to TrustSphere",
  "subject": "Welcome to TrustSphere - Get Started with vLEI",
  "ctaText": "Complete Your Profile",
  "ctaUrl": "https://trustsphere.example.com/onboarding"
}

### List all generated emails
GET {{host}}/api/email/list

### View a specific generated email (replace filename)
GET {{host}}/api/email/view/vlei_approval_email.html

